Name: Street Level: Windows Edition
About the game: Street Level is a minimalist cyberpunk themed card game, with a pulse pounding soundtrack. Gameplay consists of deciding whether to accept jobs, fights, stat upgrades, and etc., all while trying to raise your reputation level. The player wins upon reaching reputation level 12.
